**4.3 Content Preview Modal**

When you click \'Preview\' or \'Content\' on any row, a full content
modal opens showing all 9 sections:

🎯 Brief Summary --- what the content is about

🎣 Hooks --- 3 attention-grabbing openers (highlighted in orange)

🎬 Script --- timed script with timestamps \[0-2s\], \[3-7s\], etc.
(highlighted in orange)

📱 On-Screen Text --- text that appears on screen during the video

🎨 Storyboard --- visual scene descriptions

📝 Caption (Short) --- short social media caption

📄 Caption (Long) --- longer caption with hashtags

📢 CTA --- call to action (e.g., \'Download CorpFit\')

⚠️ Disclaimer --- health/safety disclaimer if needed

*Every section is editable --- click to edit, then Save Changes to
update the database directly.*

